#: /root/joao/TTMediaBot/bot/app_vars.py:11
msgid ""
"Hello! I am João Almeida. This is my fork of TTMediaBot for TeamTalk 5.\n"
"This repository focuses on stability and support for YouTube Music.\n"
"Repository: https://github.com/JoaoDEVWHADS/TTMediaBot\n"
"Original Authors: Amir Gumerov, Vladislav Kopylov, Beqa Gozalishvili, "
"Kirill Belousov.\n"
msgstr ""
"¡Hola! Soy João Almeida. Este es mi fork de TTMediaBot para TeamTalk 5.\n"
"Este repositorio se centra en la estabilidad y el soporte para YouTube "
"Music.\n"
"Repositorio: https://github.com/JoaoDEVWHADS/TTMediaBot\n"
"Autores Originales: Amir Gumerov, Vladislav Kopylov, Beqa Gozalishvili, "
"Kirill Belousov.\n"

